Privacy Policy

This game is suitable for children under the age of 13. It contains advertisements served through Google AdMob. We do not directly collect, store, or share any personal information from players, but please note that AdMob may collect certain information as described below.

Data Collection and Usage:

The game itself does not collect personal data. However, Google AdMob may collect device information, advertising identifiers, and usage data to serve personalized or non-personalized ads. These data are handled according to Google’s Privacy Policy. The game may request certain permissions required by AdMob to function properly.

Children’s Privacy:

This game is designed for children under 13 and follows COPPA (Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act) guidelines. While the game contains ads via AdMob, it does not directly collect personal information from children. AdMob may serve ads tailored to age-appropriate audiences.

Data Security:

Any information collected by AdMob is handled by Google in accordance with their privacy and security policies. The game itself does not send any player data to external servers.

Permissions:

The game may request permissions required by Google AdMob, such as access to the internet and device identifiers, to display ads. No other personal information is accessed or used by the game.

Contact:

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
